  "prompt": "How much money can I deposit in my account?",
  "response": "The amount of money you can deposit into your account generally depends on several factors, including:\n\n1. **Account Type**: Different accounts (checking, savings, business, etc.) may have different deposit limits.\n2. **Bank Policies**: Each bank or financial institution may have specific policies regarding deposit limits.\n3. **Funding Source**: There may be different limits depending on whether you're depositing cash, checks, or electronic transfers.\n4. **Regulatory Limits**: For certain types of accounts, there may be regulatory limits, such as with certain retirement accounts.\n5. **Your Account Status**: Some banks offer higher limits or fewer restrictions for customers with certain account balances or standing.\n\nTo get the most accurate information, it\u2019s best to check directly with your bank or financial institution regarding their specific policies and any applicable limits.",
